{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Chris has been so nice."},{"time":2000,"text":"I don't know how you keep it up, Chris, I really don't."},{"time":4000,"text":"So nice, all week. He's the kind of man you could say to,"},{"time":7000,"text":"\"Chris, I'm really sorry, I've crashed your car."},{"time":10000,"text":"And it gets worse, I crashed it into your house."},{"time":12000,"text":"Your house has caught fire."},{"time":14000,"text":"And what's more, your wife has just run off with your best friend.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":17000,"text":"And you know that Chris would say, \"Thank you.\""},{"time":20000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":22000,"text":"\"Thank you for sharing, that's really interesting.\""},{"time":24000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":25000,"text":"\"Thank you for taking me to a place that I didn't know existed. Thank you.\""},{"time":29000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"One of the -- (Applause) Thank you for inviting us."},{"time":33000,"text":"One of the things about appearing later on in the TED week is that,"},{"time":35000,"text":"gradually, as the days go by,"},{"time":37000,"text":"all the other speakers cover most of what you were going to say."},{"time":42000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":43000,"text":"Nuclear fusion, I had about 10 minutes on that."},{"time":47000,"text":"Spectroscopy, that was another one."},{"time":50000,"text":"Parallel universes."},{"time":52000,"text":"And so this morning I thought, \"Oh well, I'll just do a card trick.\""},{"time":56000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":58000,"text":"That one's gone as well."},{"time":60000,"text":"And today is Emmanuel's day, I think we've agreed that, already, haven't we?"},{"time":63000,"text":"Emmanuel? Absolutely. (Applause)"},{"time":66000,"text":"I was planning on finishing on a dance ..."},{"time":68000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":69000,"text":"So, that's going to look pretty shabby now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72000,"text":"So, what I thought I'd do is -- in honor of Emmanuel --"},{"time":74000,"text":"is, what I can do is to launch today the first"},{"time":78000,"text":"TED Global auction."},{"time":80000,"text":"If I could start, this is the Enigma decoding machine."},{"time":84000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":85000,"text":"Who will start me with $1,000? Anyone?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"Thank you. Bruno's face, just then,"},{"time":91000,"text":"he said, \"No, don't go through this. Don't, please don't."},{"time":93000,"text":"Don't go through this. Don't do it.\""},{"time":95000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"I'm worried. When I first got the invitation,"},{"time":102000,"text":"they said somewhere in the thing, they said, \"15 minutes to change the world,"},{"time":104000,"text":"your moment onstage.\" 15 minutes to change the world."},{"time":107000,"text":"I don't know about you, it takes me 15 minutes to change a plug."},{"time":109000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":110000,"text":"So, the idea of changing the world is really quite an extraordinary one."},{"time":114000,"text":"Well, of course now we know we don't have to change a plug,"},{"time":116000,"text":"now we've seen that wonderful demonstration"},{"time":118000,"text":"of the wireless electric -- fantastic. You know, it inspires us."},{"time":121000,"text":"300 years ago he'd have been burnt at the stake for that."},{"time":124000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":125000,"text":"And now it's an idea."},{"time":127000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":128000,"text":"It's great. It's fantastic."},{"time":130000,"text":"But you do meet some fantastic people,"},{"time":132000,"text":"people who look at the world in a totally different way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134000,"text":"Yesterday, David Deutsch, another one"},{"time":136000,"text":"who covered most of what I was going to say."},{"time":138000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":140000,"text":"But when you think of the world in that way,"},{"time":142000,"text":"it does make going to Starbucks a whole new experience, don't you think?"},{"time":145000,"text":"I mean, he must walk in and they will say,"},{"time":147000,"text":"\"Would you like a macchiato,"},{"time":149000,"text":"or a latte, or an Americano,"},{"time":151000,"text":"or a cappuccino?\""},{"time":153000,"text":"And he'll say,"},{"time":155000,"text":"\"You're offering me things that are infinitely variable.\""},{"time":158000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":160000,"text":"\"How can your coffee be true?\""},{"time":162000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":164000,"text":"And they will say,"},{"time":166000,"text":"\"Would you mind if I serve the next customer?\""},{"time":168000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":170000,"text":"And Elaine Morgan yesterday, wasn't she wonderful?"},{"time":172000,"text":"Fantastic. Really good."},{"time":174000,"text":"Her talk about the aquatic ape, and the link, of course,"},{"time":176000,"text":"the link between Darwinism"},{"time":179000,"text":"and the fact that we are all naked beneath this --"},{"time":181000,"text":"we're not hirsute and we can swim rather well."},{"time":184000,"text":"And she said, you know, she's 90. She's running out of time, she said."},{"time":186000,"text":"And she's desperate to find more evidence for the link."},{"time":189000,"text":"And I think, \"I'm sitting next to Lewis Pugh.\""},{"time":191000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":192000,"text":"This man has swum around the North Pole, what more evidence do you want?"},{"time":196000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":198000,"text":"And there he is."},{"time":200000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":201000,"text":"That's how TED brings these connections together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"I wasn't here on Tuesday. I didn't actually see Gordon Brown's"},{"time":205000,"text":"job application -- um, sorry."},{"time":207000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":208000,"text":"I'm so sorry. (Applause)"},{"time":210000,"text":"I'm so sorry. No, no. (Applause)"},{"time":212000,"text":"No, no, ahh ... (Applause)"},{"time":216000,"text":"(As Brown): \"Global problems require Scottish solutions.\""},{"time":220000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":222000,"text":"The problem I have is because Gordon Brown, he comes onstage"},{"time":224000,"text":"and he looks for all the world like a man"},{"time":226000,"text":"who's just taken the head off a bear suit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228000,"text":"(As Brown): \"Hello, can I tell you what happened in the woods back there?"},{"time":233000,"text":"Uh, no.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":235000,"text":"\"I'm sorry. I've only got 18 minutes, 18 minutes to talk about saving the world,"},{"time":240000,"text":"saving the planet, global institutions."},{"time":242000,"text":"Our work on climate change,"},{"time":244000,"text":"I've only got 18 minutes, unfortunately I'm not able to tell you about"},{"time":247000,"text":"all the wonderful things we're doing to promote the climate change agenda"},{"time":251000,"text":"in Great Britain,"},{"time":253000,"text":"like the third runway we're planning at Heathrow Airport ...\""},{"time":256000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":259000,"text":"\"The large coal-fired power station we're building"},{"time":261000,"text":"at King's North,"},{"time":263000,"text":"and of course the exciting news that only today,"},{"time":265000,"text":"only this week, Britain's only manufacturer"},{"time":268000,"text":"of wind turbines has been forced to close."},{"time":271000,"text":"No time, unfortunately,"},{"time":273000,"text":"to mention those.\""},{"time":275000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":279000,"text":"\"British jobs for Scottish people ..."},{"time":282000,"text":"No.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":286000,"text":"\"Christian principles, Christian values."},{"time":288000,"text":"Thou shalt not kill, thou shalt not steal,"},{"time":291000,"text":"thou shalt not covet thy neighbor's wife.\""},{"time":293000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":296000,"text":"\"Although to be honest, when I was at Number 11 that was never going to be a problem.\""},{"time":299000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":302000,"text":"(As Tony Blair): \"Yeah, alright, come on, eh."},{"time":306000,"text":"Alright Gordon, come on, eh."},{"time":308000,"text":"I just, can I just say a few things about,"},{"time":310000,"text":"first about Cherie, because she's a wonderful lady,"},{"time":312000,"text":"my wife, with a wonderful smile."},{"time":316000,"text":"That reminds me, I must post that letter.\""},{"time":318000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":320000,"text":"\"I just think, you know, what people forget,"},{"time":322000,"text":"Gordon and I, we always got on perfectly well."},{"time":325000,"text":"Alright, it was never exactly 'Brokeback Mountain.'\""},{"time":328000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":331000,"text":"\"You know, I wrote to him, just before I left office. I said,"},{"time":333000,"text":"'Can I rely on your support for the next month?'"},{"time":335000,"text":"And he wrote back. He said, 'No, you can't.'"},{"time":339000,"text":"Which kind of surprised me, because I'd never seen 'can't' spelled that way before.\""},{"time":342000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"Another thing Gordon could have mentioned in his speech"},{"time":349000,"text":"to the Mansion House in 2002 --"},{"time":352000,"text":"that was to the building; the people weren't listening."},{"time":354000,"text":"But the people, when talking about the finance industry, he said,"},{"time":356000,"text":"\"What you as the city of London have done for financial services,"},{"time":362000,"text":"we, as a government, hope to do for the economy as a whole.\""},{"time":365000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":368000,"text":"When you think what's happened to financial services,"},{"time":370000,"text":"and you see what's happened to the economy, you think,"},{"time":372000,"text":"\"Well, there is a man who delivers on his promises.\""},{"time":374000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":375000,"text":"But we're in a new world now. We're in a completely new world."},{"time":377000,"text":"This is the first time that I can remember, where if you get a letter"},{"time":379000,"text":"from the bank manager about a loan, you don't know if you're borrowing"},{"time":381000,"text":"money from him, or if he's borrowing money from you."},{"time":383000,"text":"Am I right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":385000,"text":"These extraordinary things, Icelandic Internet accounts."},{"time":387000,"text":"Did anyone here have an Icelandic Internet account?"},{"time":390000,"text":"Why would you do that? Why would -- It's like one step up"},{"time":392000,"text":"from replying to one of those emails from Nigeria, isn't it?"},{"time":395000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":396000,"text":"Asking for your bank details."},{"time":398000,"text":"And, you know, Iceland, it was never going to cut it."},{"time":401000,"text":"It didn't have that kind of collateral."},{"time":403000,"text":"What does it have? It has fish, that's all."},{"time":406000,"text":"That's why the Prime Minister went on television. He said,"},{"time":408000,"text":"\"This has left us all"},{"time":410000,"text":"with a very big haddock.\""},{"time":412000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":416000,"text":"A lot of what I do -- I have to try and make sense"},{"time":418000,"text":"of things before I can make nonsense of them."},{"time":420000,"text":"And making sense of the financial crisis is very, very difficult."},{"time":423000,"text":"Luckily, somebody like George Bush was really helpful."},{"time":425000,"text":"He summed it up, really, at a dinner."},{"time":427000,"text":"He was speaking at a dinner, he said,"},{"time":430000,"text":"\"Wall Street got drunk.\""},{"time":432000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":434000,"text":"\"And now it's got a hangover.\""},{"time":437000,"text":"And that's, you know, that's something --"},{"time":439000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":444000,"text":"And that's something we can relate to."},{"time":446000,"text":"It's certainly something he can relate to."},{"time":448000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":450000,"text":"And the other one, of course, is Donald Rumsfeld, who said,"},{"time":452000,"text":"\"There are the known knowns, the things we know we know."},{"time":456000,"text":"And then you got the known unknowns,"},{"time":459000,"text":"the things we know we don't know."},{"time":461000,"text":"And then you got the unknown unknowns, those are the things"},{"time":463000,"text":"we don't know we don't know.\""},{"time":465000,"text":"And being English, when I first heard that I thought, \"What a load of cock.\""},{"time":467000,"text":"And then, you're now, well, actually, that's what this is about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472000,"text":"This whole, what Ben Bernanke has said,"},{"time":474000,"text":"the chaotic unwinding of the world's financial system,"},{"time":478000,"text":"it's about -- they don't know, they didn't know what they were doing."},{"time":481000,"text":"In 2006, the head of the American Mortgage Bankers Association said, quote,"},{"time":485000,"text":"\"As we can clearly see,"},{"time":489000,"text":"no seismic occurrence"},{"time":491000,"text":"is about to overwhelm the U.S. economy.\""},{"time":493000,"text":"Now, there is a man on top of his job."},{"time":495000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":496000,"text":"And when the crisis was happening, the head of quantitative equities"},{"time":498000,"text":"at Lehman Brothers said,"},{"time":500000,"text":"\"Events which models predicted would happen"},{"time":503000,"text":"once every 10,000 years"},{"time":505000,"text":"happened every day for three days.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":508000,"text":"So, it's extraordinary. It's a new world that's very, very difficult to make sense of."},{"time":511000,"text":"But we have a new hope. We have a new man."},{"time":515000,"text":"America has now elected its first openly black President."},{"time":518000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":520000,"text":"Wonderful news."},{"time":522000,"text":"Not only that, he's left-handed. Have you noticed this?"},{"time":524000,"text":"How many people here are left-handed?"},{"time":526000,"text":"You see, a lot of the people that I most admire,"},{"time":528000,"text":"they're great artists, great designers, great thinkers,"},{"time":530000,"text":"they're left-handed."},{"time":532000,"text":"And somebody said to me last night, you know, being left-handed,"},{"time":534000,"text":"you have to learn to write without smudging the ink."},{"time":538000,"text":"And somebody was talking about metaphors on Monday."},{"time":540000,"text":"And I thought, what a wonderful metaphor, isn't it? An American President who"},{"time":542000,"text":"has to write without smudging the ink."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545000,"text":"You like that one? As opposed to you could see"},{"time":547000,"text":"George Bush, well, what's the metaphor there?"},{"time":550000,"text":"I think it would be something out of the aquatic ape thing, wouldn't it?"},{"time":552000,"text":"\"Well, you know I'm sorry about that."},{"time":554000,"text":"I'm right-handed but I seem to have smudged that ink as well.\""},{"time":557000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":559000,"text":"But, you know, he's gone. Now he's gone."},{"time":561000,"text":"That's eight years of American History, eight minutes of my act,"},{"time":563000,"text":"just gone like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565000,"text":"\"You know, it's the end of an error [sic]."},{"time":567000,"text":"I happen to believe it was a great error."},{"time":570000,"text":"I know folks said to me they believe it was one of the greatest errors"},{"time":572000,"text":"in the history of the United States."},{"time":575000,"text":"But we proved them wrong in Iraq."},{"time":578000,"text":"They said there was no link between Iraq and Al Qaeda."},{"time":581000,"text":"There is now.\""},{"time":583000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":584000,"text":"\"But I have a message for the suicide bombers,"},{"time":587000,"text":"for those people who've blown themselves up.\""},{"time":590000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":593000,"text":"\"We're going to find you.\""},{"time":595000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":596000,"text":"\"We're going to make sure you don't do it again.\""},{"time":598000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":599000,"text":"But now he's gone, and it's great to see one of the --"},{"time":601000,"text":"arguably one of the worst speech makers"},{"time":603000,"text":"in American history,"},{"time":605000,"text":"now given way to one of the greatest, in Obama."},{"time":607000,"text":"You were there, maybe, on the night of his victory."},{"time":609000,"text":"And he spoke to the crowd in Chicago, he said,"},{"time":612000,"text":"\"If there is anyone out there"},{"time":617000,"text":"who still doubts"},{"time":620000,"text":"that America is a place"},{"time":625000,"text":"where all things are possible ...\""},{"time":627000,"text":"I can't do the whole thing because it would take too long, it really would."},{"time":629000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":630000,"text":"But you get the picture. And then it goes to the inauguration."},{"time":634000,"text":"And he and the Chief Justice, they trip over each other,"},{"time":636000,"text":"they get their words wrong and they screw the thing up."},{"time":638000,"text":"And there is George Bush sitting there going, \"Heh heh heh heh ...\""},{"time":640000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":641000,"text":"\"Not so easy is it? Heh heh heh.\""},{"time":643000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":645000,"text":"But the interesting thing is, Gordon Brown was talking about Cicero,"},{"time":648000,"text":"who said, people would listen to a speech, they said, \"Great speech.\""},{"time":650000,"text":"And then they'd listen to Demosthenes,"},{"time":652000,"text":"and they'd say, \"Let's march.\""},{"time":654000,"text":"And we all want to believe in President Obama."},{"time":657000,"text":"It's rather like that line in the film \"As Good As it Gets.\""},{"time":660000,"text":"Do you remember that film with Helen Hunt and Jack Nicholson,"},{"time":662000,"text":"and Helen Hunt says to Jack Nicholson, \"What do you see in me?\""},{"time":665000,"text":"And Jack Nicholson just says,"},{"time":667000,"text":"\"You make me want to be a better man.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":670000,"text":"And you want a leader who inspires and challenges"},{"time":672000,"text":"and makes you want to be a better citizen. Right?"},{"time":675000,"text":"But at the moment, it's a Cicero thing."},{"time":677000,"text":"We like what Barack Obama says, but we don't do anything about it."},{"time":679000,"text":"So he comes over to this country, and he says,"},{"time":682000,"text":"\"We need"},{"time":684000,"text":"a big fiscal stimulus.\""},{"time":687000,"text":"And everyone goes, \"Great!\" He leaves the country"},{"time":689000,"text":"and the French and the Germans go, \"No, no, forget about that,"},{"time":692000,"text":"absolutely not.\" Nothing happens. He goes to Strasburg."},{"time":694000,"text":"He says, \"We need more boots on the ground in Afghanistan.\""},{"time":698000,"text":"And everyone goes, \"Great idea.\""},{"time":700000,"text":"He leaves, people go, \"No no no, we're not going to do that."},{"time":702000,"text":"5,000 maximum, and no rockets. No, no, not going to do it.\""},{"time":705000,"text":"He goes to Prague, he says, \"We believe in a nuclear-free world.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":708000,"text":"And it's great to have an American president who can say the word \"nuclear,\""},{"time":711000,"text":"let's just point that out first."},{"time":713000,"text":"Do you remember that? George Bush, \"A nu-ca-ler.\""},{"time":715000,"text":"Sorry, what? \"A nu-ca-ler.\""},{"time":718000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":719000,"text":"Could you say \"avuncular\"? \"Avunclear.\""},{"time":722000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":723000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725000,"text":"But he says, \"We want a nuclear-free world.\""},{"time":727000,"text":"And that day, North Korea, that very day,"},{"time":729000,"text":"North Korea is just seeing if it can"},{"time":731000,"text":"just get one over Japan --"},{"time":734000,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":735000,"text":"and land it before ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":737000,"text":"So, where do we look for inspiration? We've still got Bill Clinton."},{"time":740000,"text":"\"Travels the world.\" (Laughs)"},{"time":743000,"text":"\"I believe, I believe it was President Dwight D. Eisenhower who said ...\""},{"time":750000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":751000,"text":"\"Tell a lie; it was Diana Ross ...\""},{"time":753000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":754000,"text":"\"... who said, reach out and touch ...\""},{"time":757000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":759000,"text":"\"... somebody's gla -- hand.\""},{"time":761000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":763000,"text":"\"Make this world a better place, if you can."},{"time":766000,"text":"I just think that's important. I really do."},{"time":769000,"text":"And I was hoping Hillary would get to the White House,"},{"time":771000,"text":"because she'd have been out of our home for four years."},{"time":773000,"text":"And I, you know.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":775000,"text":"\"So, when that didn't work out I had to make a few arrangements, let me tell you.\""},{"time":778000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":780000,"text":"So, there's him. In Britain we have Prince Charles:"},{"time":782000,"text":"\"And the environment is so important, all we can do."},{"time":785000,"text":"My wife gets fed up with me constantly trying to"},{"time":788000,"text":"push emissions up her agenda.\""},{"time":790000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":792000,"text":"Or, any South Africans, we have Mandela to inspire."},{"time":797000,"text":"Mandela, the great man Mandela."},{"time":799000,"text":"He's been honored with a statue now."},{"time":801000,"text":"The previous highest honor he had in Britain"},{"time":803000,"text":"was a visit from the team from Ground Force, a gardening program."},{"time":806000,"text":"\"So, Nelson, how would you like a nice water feature?\""},{"time":810000,"text":"\"Ahh, listen to me Mr. Titchmarsh.\""},{"time":814000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":816000,"text":"\"I was held in prison"},{"time":821000,"text":"for nearly 30 years"},{"time":824000,"text":"on an island"},{"time":826000,"text":"in the middle of the ocean."},{"time":829000,"text":"Why would I need a bloody water feature?\""},{"time":832000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":834000,"text":"Very quickly: I wasn't quite sure how to end this talk"},{"time":838000,"text":"and then yesterday that man came up with a wonderful quote"},{"time":841000,"text":"from the \"Japanese Essays on Idleness\""},{"time":843000,"text":"which said it's nice to have something which is unfinished"},{"time":845000,"text":"because it implies there is still room for growth."},{"time":848000,"text":"Thank you very much indeed."},{"time":850000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}